{"tid":1766651,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[聲討黃絲] 明明茂名單野係完美既理論武裝 我唔明點解無人用","createTime":"2019-12-02T18:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T14:43:01.000Z","uid":119393,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c46b318214001c0a7e7e21acd1ebdd2356228d8f","tid":1766651,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T18:06:38.000Z","msg":"香港政府既劇本係不斷講你地香港示威者好暴力, 係暴徒, 要割席, <br />\n持續削減你地支持者人數令呢個運動自然消滅<br />\n到時共產黨又可以同侵侵邀功冇出動軍隊<br />\n<br />\n茂名示威呢單野既出現, 明明係天賜比香港反送中運動既禮物<br />\n但我響連登見到既回應係<br />\n&quot;之後咪一樣秋後算帳~&quot;<br />\n&quot;又一單, 成日都有架啦~&quot;<br />\n&quot;咪講同茂名connect呀~&quot;<br />\n...之類<br />\n<br />\n香港傳媒響報導呢單新聞上, 除左毒果較為詳盡外<br />\n其他都輕輕帶過話&quot;廣東茂名因為建造火葬場引起衝突&quot;<br />\n特別係淡化茂名抗爭者既暴力程度, <br />\n即係沿途火燒警崗, 破壞政府車輛/警車, 佔領當地政府大樓捉人出去打, 更加唔會有圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGQts8A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGQts8A.jpg&h=66a5d828&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aenjzOB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaenjzOB.jpg&h=af50de77&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔信既話你地可以去任何一間圖書館既電腦search下呢單新聞比較下各傳媒點報...<br />\n<br />\n我知道連登仔好多得把口所以貼埋今年公信力插水既TVB果篇比你地睇:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5de25a06e603832a473aed2b/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E8%8C%82%E5%90%8D%E6%9C%89%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%BB%BA%E7%81%AB%E8%91%AC%E5%A0%B4-%E8%88%87%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E7%88%86%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fgreaterchina%2F5de25a06e603832a473aed2b%2F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%258C%2582%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%2591%25AC%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRcLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=b934e55b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5de25a06e603832a473aed2b/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E8%8C%82%E5%90%8D%E6%9C%89%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%BB%BA%E7%81%AB%E8%91%AC%E5%A0%B4-%E8%88%87%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E7%88%86%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81</a><br />\n<blockquote>廣東茂名有民眾不滿地方政府興建火葬場，與警方爆發衝突。<br />\n<br />\n網上圖片見到，有民眾舉起標語，反對文樓鎮興建火葬場；亦有網上片段聲稱拍攝到周四，防暴警察到場，並施放催淚彈驅散人群，有民眾在衝突中受傷。<br />\n<br />\n根據網上社交媒體帖文，茂名文樓鎮的民眾不滿政府以建設人文生態園為名徵地，實際是興建火葬場，周四上街抗議。<br />\n<br />\n社交媒體亦流傳一份周五發出但未經證實的政府公告，指由於項目有不同意見，當局決定停止建設；又指任何擾亂公共秩序的打砸搶破壞活動，公安機關將依法打擊嚴懲。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你地再比較下毒果果篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20191130/XI64G2W6TRNE27RPYDACGAU72I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191130%2FXI64G2W6TRNE27RPYDACGAU72I%2F&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRcLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=e56d6712\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191130%2FXI64G2W6TRNE27RPYDACGAU72I%2F&h=cc29a05f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20191130/XI64G2W6TRNE27RPYDACGAU72I/</a><br />\n<br />\n我相信智力在水平線上既香港人心裡都會明白傳媒點解要淡化茂名單野<br />\n因為正好完美反駁香港政府&quot;香港示威好暴力 要割席&quot;呢個論點<br />\n人地頭尾只係四日已經攪掂<br />\n第一日政府公布準備起既生態公園其實係火葬場<br />\n第二日當地居民聯名上書反對<br />\n第三日見政府無回應, 當地居民進軍市政府總部, 沿途燒毀警崗, 破壞警車, 佔領政府大樓, 捉人去打, 示威者仲話香港人軟弱, 係反面教材(好似係, 我唔fact check lol)<br />\n第四日當地宣布不會起火葬場<br />\n香港呢, 香港攪左半年達成度先20%<br />\n<br />\n我希望所有黃絲都記住呢單野<br />\n以後同藍絲爭執比人話暴力時可以反駁, 如:<br />\n&quot;你知唔知我地比中國人鬧太軟弱, 係反面教材?&quot;<br />\n&quot;茂名細所以不值一提? 茂名面積有30個香港咁大...&quot;<br />\n&quot;茂名人少所以不值一提? 茂名人口超過600萬...&quot;<br />\n&quot;你冇聽過呢單野? 因為香港政府既劇本係香港示威好暴力麻, 點可以報中國人鬧香港示威軟弱&quot;"},{"pid":"b99884266fe1ce5710458d2c7b6d2bf64d8c52aa","tid":1766651,"uid":50873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T18:22:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15306a54dd07c65ea684b7e03de59d4ff1062c5a","tid":1766651,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T18:25:06.000Z","msg":"習曱甴推"},{"pid":"7bb3d18f9c1a1d3fa009c308036dc514e47446bd","tid":1766651,"uid":135740,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T18:25:10.000Z","msg":"係wor 屌!!!!<br />\n<br />\n大地中國人暴力過我地 同共產黨正面交峰都贏到 過程都係用暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地用暴力成功 <br />\n我地要成功都不得不靠暴力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb20fc99c2c5667910e9bf5403b287a705df9dff","tid":1766651,"uid":185121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T18:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係 人哋仲要成功爭取"},{"pid":"bbe808cacb8191ecd4e0f830b74343b112fe1d3d","tid":1766651,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T18:25:52.000Z","msg":"[黃色經濟圈] 時代革命由生活開始：黃色商圈已降臨（劉細良）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1766519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1766519</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4be87e59f7b4fa93f941343091d48715865f5290","tid":1766651,"uid":40606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T18:28:15.000Z","m